metadata.name: PsyDucks #1
metadata.description: PSY is a lottery system implemented on the blockchain - (Win upto 10000 ETH). PsyDucks is the first in a series of 4 collections that will be released back to back. The 4 collections will be released in 4 different phases (3 collections totalling 70,000 tokens and one Open Edition collection). Anyone holding any of the 70,000 token will qualify for the lottery, the ID of your tokens you hold will act as the numbers you choose for the lottery. All tokens apart from being considered for the jackpot will also give you returns some return - by trading one of our tokens you can will upto 10% of the total trade volume for that collection. Half of the money that is made from all the NFT collections will be added into a lotto pool. The lotto pool will live in its own contract, the jackpot winner will be added to the contract and only the winner can release funds from the lotto pool.For more information checkout our website.
